Package project2

Class ticket

java.lang.Object
project2.ticket
public class ticket
extends java.lang.Object
This is a ticket class/object The movie class has two fields type: is the type of ticket in this case all tickets will be general admission tickets, this field is a string. rank: this is the rank or level of priority of this ticket. This filed is an int the level of priority can be from 1 to 100. 100 being the highest level of priority and 1 being the lowest level of priority.
Author:
Sahara Karima Mosin Rahimani
